What should we do if there is lagging occured during projecting the videos? Helpful question! For the lagging issue, we first advise you to change the network into 5G WIFI, or if you don't have 5G WiFi, anycast adapter will help, too How long should we clean the air filter of this projector? Good question! For a better maintenance of GO1 projector with wifi and bluetooth, it is better to clean the filter 1-3months a time. How can I get a clear and sharp picture? 1. Please wait a little while when autofocusing, do not press any buttons. 2. You can also use the F+/F- adjustment on the remote control to get better focusing effect. Why does the projector have sound but no picture when I mirror the screen? 1. Samsung phones: Please enable HDCP in settings and try again. 2. Other phones: Netflix, Amazon Prime and Hulu are not supported on all projectors due to HDCP copyright issues, but you can enjoy them with a TV stick. How can I hang the projector from the ceiling? 1. Remove the four footpads from the bottom of the projector. 2. Screw the ceiling mount into the holes (1/4" screw) under the footpads. 3. Rotate the video so that it plays the right way up.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great purchase for home movie nights
reviews.reviewText: I love how compact the size is, making it super easy to carry and move around. To be honest I didn’t expect much about the picture quality with the price and size of this projector at the beginning, but turns out the image quality is very good with sharp resolution and accurate and bright colors. The set up process is very easy and only takes short time to connect with my phone/ipad/laptop. I love how it auto focuses to the wall and has two options to change settings with (remote controller&on the projector). Overall a great purchase for me, I was originally use it just for movie nights but also found out it’s great to play video games or watch TikTok’s with too. The build in speaker also has pretty good sound quality and I’m happy for this purchase & has already recommended to friends who has similar needs.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 1, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to install and good picture quality also good sound from the projector.
reviews.reviewText: Unboxing setting up the projector was a simple procedure. All the wires and accessories were of good quality. The best part of the projector is the auto focus option. When you move closer or farther to the screen, it automatically adjusts the image qualityThe sound the projector makes is very minimal. Fan is designed to be quit when compared to my earlier projector of the similar class. Remote has all the features which the buttons on the projects can do. It is easy to use remote. Manual which came with the box is pretty easy to understand. The sound is loud enough, so you don't need an extra speaker. It comes with multiple connection options such as HDMI, USB, and Bluetooth, and offers effortless screen mirroring from both iPhone and android devices. Overall, I'm extremely satisfied with the purchase.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Keystone and auto focus works well enough, but is definitely not "automatic"
reviews.reviewText: I have this in the corner of my ceiling in the bedroom (so as to not fall on my head while I sleep), and I was able to keystone it manually to fit nicely, and it remembers the shape, and auto focuses. The tradeoff is the left half of the screen is blurrier than the right side. It's certainly not magically automatic like it showed in a video, but it does the job. Also I have to select HDMI every time by pressing, down, down, left, ok, ok to switch to the computer, which is mildly annoying. I would go back and spend twice as much and hope for better quality, but it does the job. Also the built in speaker isn't terrible, but I use good speakers anyway.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 3, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good WiFI projector
reviews.reviewText: Purchased this wireless projector to use in my bedroom. The setup is pretty easy and simple. I like that it also comes with RJ-45 port just in case I want better network connection. It has two HDMI ports, a USB port, and a AV and headphone ports. I was able to pair the projector with my iPhone after connecting to the home network. It’s pretty smooth. Lastly, I like that I can just play the movies from my plugged-in external hard drive, and the quality is high 1080, provided the fact that I didn’t even use a projector screen. Overall, it’s a good product for this price.
